rows.label: qev085910_MSG0001
rows.name: Welcome to Army Pizza! You here for a pie?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085910_MSG0002
rows.name:
...Whazza? You need 10 delivered ASAP?
No sweat. For just 10,000 credits, we'll send your
piping-hot pizzas anywhere in New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085910_JNK0010
rows.name: Purchase

rows.label: qev085910_SEL0011
rows.name: Buy the pizzas for 10,000 credits.

rows.label: qev085910_JNK0020
rows.name: Wait

rows.label: qev085910_SEL0021
rows.name: Hold off for now.

rows.label: qev085910_MSG0003
rows.name: These are headed out to Jeshero's place, yeah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085910_MSG0009
rows.name: We'll have 'em there before the cheese begins to cool![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085910_MSG0004
rows.name:
Hey now, passing up my pizza's like missing out on all
the good things in life! ...Or at least half of 'em.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085910_MSG0011
rows.name:
...Hey! What're you trying to pull here, bub?
You ain't got the cash![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085910_MSG0012
rows.name:
If you wanna sink your teeth into my pies,
come back with 10 large first![ST:wait ]
